dc_description_s: This data represents addresses for Waushara County, Wisconsin in 2019.[This data set was developed initially automated by the WI Department of Natural Resources. It is updated and on an on-going basis, by Waushara County. The data contained in this file only covers points address information managed by the County.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: https://waushara.maps.arcgis.com/home/index.html#
